    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/4d1fd7d518ea23bbdf236662e2969bff.avif?t=1769957979\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras_big/4d1fd7d518ea23bbdf236662e2969bff.webp?t=1769957979 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一场无法醒来的噩梦，一段难以抚平的疼痛...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款独特的生存恐怖游戏中，古典音乐与心理恐怖交织，营造出令人窒息的阴森氛围。你将扮演普通女孩爱丽丝，一觉醒来，发现自己被困在一个不断变化的诡异世界中。冰雪覆盖的孤儿院、潜伏在暗处的怪物、错综复杂的谜题——每一步都充满危机与未知。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了生存，你必须收集物资、躲避追杀，并解开隐藏在黑暗中的秘密。然而，随着真相逐渐浮出水面，你是否能承受这一切背后的残酷现实？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这款游戏的玩法有：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/b628f08c27fb52dbc0425783304ebc4f.poster.avif?t=1769957979\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/b628f08c27fb52dbc0425783304ebc4f.webm?t=1769957979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/b628f08c27fb52dbc0425783304ebc4f.mp4?t=1769957979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动作射击</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用不同的枪械武器击败敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>地图探索</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一步步探索诡异恐怖的孤儿院，获得不同的道具来解锁不同的探索区域，同时在探索的途中还要应对可能突然出现的不明所以的变化</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>资源管理</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集并合理利用有限的资源，想尽办法生存下来</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解谜推理</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜集信息，解开各种各样的谜题，并从中找到最后的真相</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/5a5d4403eac28db82baf24563011b649.poster.avif?t=1769957979\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/5a5d4403eac28db82baf24563011b649.webm?t=1769957979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/5a5d4403eac28db82baf24563011b649.mp4?t=1769957979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
